  <summary date="2017-04-26T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Medical Device Safety Act

This bill amends the Federal Food, Drug, and Cosmetic Act to declare that an action for damages or a person's liability under state law is not affected by the federal prohibition on state or local requirements regarding medical devices. This bill is retroactively effective and applies to pending civil actions.</summary>
